#
# <body (optional - explain WHY, not WHAT)>
#
# <footer (optional - reference issues, breaking changes)>
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Commit Message Guidelines for Arteterapia Project
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# BEFORE COMMITTING: Ensure changes align with .agent/AGENT_GUIDELINES.md
#
# Types:
#   feat      - New feature
#   fix       - Bug fix
#   docs      - Documentation changes
#   refactor  - Code refactoring (no functional change)
#   test      - Adding or updating tests
#   chore     - Maintenance tasks (dependencies, config)
#   i18n      - Translation updates
#   db        - Database model or migration changes
#   security  - Security-related changes
#   ui        - UI/UX improvements
#
# Subject:
#   - Use imperative mood ("Add feature" not "Added feature")
#   - No period at the end
#   - Keep under 50 characters
#   - Be specific and descriptive
#
# Body:
#   - Explain WHY, not WHAT (code shows what)
#   - Wrap at 72 characters
#   - Separate from subject with blank line
#   - Use bullet points for multiple changes
#
# Examples:
#   feat: Add participant age filtering in workshop detail view
#
#   fix: Resolve language switcher session persistence bug
#   
#   The session['lang'] was not being set correctly when using
#   the language switcher. Updated the /lang/<code> route to
#   properly store the selection before redirect.
#
#   db: Add cascade delete to Session-Observation relationship
#   
#   When a session is deleted, orphaned observations were remaining
#   in the database. Added CASCADE on delete to observation foreign key
#   to automatically clean up related records.
#
#   i18n: Update English translations for authentication module
#   
#   Resolves #15
#
# Footer:
#   - Reference issues: "Fixes #123" or "Closes #45"
#   - Note breaking changes: "BREAKING CHANGE: ..."
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Remember:
#   ✅ Read .agent/AGENT_GUIDELINES.md before contributing
#   ✅ Use workflows in .agent/workflows/ for common tasks
#   ✅ Test both Spanish and English
#   ✅ Verify Admin and Editor perspectives
#   ❌ Never commit .env, .db, or .mo files
#   ❌ Never modify observation question IDs if data exists
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
